<img alt="image" height="197" src="https://bia-facile.fr/manuel-bia-2021_files/Image_238.png" width="551"/></p>
<p class="s22">
              Figure 1.66.</p>
<p></p>
<p>
<img alt="image" height="257" src="https://bia-facile.fr/manuel-bia-2021_files/Image_239.jpg" width="327"/></p>
<p class="s22">
              Figure 1.67.</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
<img alt="image" height="271" src="https://bia-facile.fr/manuel-bia-2021_files/Image_240.jpg" width="386"/></p>
<p class="s22">
              Figure 1.68.</p>
