</td>
<td>
<p class="s51">
                      Induced Drag</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</li>
<li data-list-text="II.">
<p class="s17">
<a name="bookmark116"></a>‌Mechanics of flight</p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
<p><img alt="image" height="216" src="https://bia-facile.fr/manuel-bia-2021_files/Image_241.jpg" width="412"/></p>
